ygData.messageBody:
I believe in the power of the mind.
I want people to share the results that they have achieved using
thought control, affirmations and the pure power of their minds. Does
belief really work ? If you know that it does, share your experiences.
I want to learn. I want to hear about techniques that work. I want to
hear of the results that people have achieved using the pure power
of their minds.
Please join www.egroups.com/group/MindPowerResults
